# Plan: Add `@ai-sdk/pixelart` Provider

## Context

The task is to add a new fictional "PixelArt" AI provider to the Vercel AI SDK monorepo. This provider only supports image generation (no language models, no embeddings, no speech, no transcription). It follows the exact same package structure as `packages/fal` — the closest analog since FAL also focuses on image/media generation rather than text. The new package will be named `@ai-sdk/pixelart` and live at `packages/pixelart/`.

Key specifics:
- Factory function: `createPixelArt` (default singleton: `pixelArt`)
- Base URL: `https://api.pixelart.ai/v1`
- API key env var: `PIXELART_API_KEY`
- Provider-specific image options (via `providerOptions.pixelart`): `style` (`"pixel" | "retro" | "8bit"`) and `pixelDensity` (number)
- Standard image options supported: `size`, `aspectRatio`, `seed`, `n`, `prompt`
- API endpoint: `POST /images/generate`
- Response format: `{ created: number, data: [{ b64_json: string }] }`

---

## Critical Files to Reference (Read-only, do NOT modify)

| File | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `packages/fal/package.json` | Package.json template |
| `packages/fal/tsconfig.json` | Tsconfig template |
| `packages/fal/tsconfig.build.json` | Build tsconfig template |
| `packages/fal/tsup.config.ts` | Tsup config template |
| `packages/fal/vitest.node.config.js` | Vitest node config template |
| `packages/fal/vitest.edge.config.js` | Vitest edge config template |
| `packages/fal/src/fal-provider.ts` | Provider factory pattern |
| `packages/fal/src/fal-image-model.ts` | Image model class pattern |
| `packages/fal/src/fal-image-settings.ts` | Model ID type pattern |
| `packages/fal/src/fal-image-options.ts` | Provider options schema pattern |
| `packages/fal/src/index.ts` | Exports pattern |
| `packages/fal/src/version.ts` | Version pattern |
| `packages/provider/src/image-model/v3/image-model-v3.ts` | `ImageModelV3` interface |
| `packages/provider/src/image-model/v3/image-model-v3-call-options.ts` | Call options interface |
| `tsconfig.json` | Root project references (to add entry) |

---

## Files to Create (New Only)

```
packages/pixelart/
├── package.json
├── tsconfig.json
├── tsconfig.build.json
├── tsup.config.ts
├── vitest.node.config.js
├── vitest.edge.config.js
└── src/
    ├── index.ts
    ├── version.ts
    ├── pixelart-provider.ts
    ├── pixelart-image-model.ts
    ├── pixelart-image-settings.ts
    ├── pixelart-image-options.ts
    └── pixelart-image-model.test.ts
```

---

## File to Modify

- `tsconfig.json` (root) — add `{ "path": "packages/pixelart" }` in alphabetical order between `packages/perplexity` and `packages/provider`

---

## Step-by-Step Implementation

### Step 1 — `packages/pixelart/package.json`

Mirrors `packages/fal/package.json` exactly. Key differences:
- `"name": "@ai-sdk/pixelart"`
- `"version": "0.0.0"` (new package)
- Remove `prepack`/`postpack` scripts (no docs file yet)
- Keep all other fields identical (scripts, exports, dependencies, devDependencies, peerDependencies, engines, publishConfig)

```json
{
  "name": "@ai-sdk/pixelart",
  "version": "0.0.0",
  "license": "Apache-2.0",
  "sideEffects": false,
  "main": "./dist/index.js",
  "module": "./dist/index.mjs",
  "types": "./dist/index.d.ts",
  "files": [
    "dist/**/*",
    "src",
    "!src/**/*.test.ts",
    "!src/**/*.test-d.ts",
    "!src/**/__snapshots__",
    "!src/**/__fixtures__",
    "CHANGELOG.md",
    "README.md"
  ],
  "scripts": {
    "build": "pnpm clean && tsup --tsconfig tsconfig.build.json",
    "build:watch": "pnpm clean && tsup --watch",
    "clean": "del-cli dist *.tsbuildinfo",
    "type-check": "tsc --build",
    "test": "pnpm test:node && pnpm test:edge",
    "test:update": "pnpm test:node -u",
    "test:watch": "vitest --config vitest.node.config.js",
    "test:edge": "vitest --config vitest.edge.config.js --run",
    "test:node": "vitest --config vitest.node.config.js --run"
  },
  "exports": {
    "./package.json": "./package.json",
    ".": {
      "types": "./dist/index.d.ts",
